          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Domestic Violence Safety Plan Grant Program Act of 2017</b> <strong>or</strong> <b>My Sister's Keeper Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Justice to award grants to eligible state and local governments, educational institutions, and non-profit organizations to develop, promote, and teach the importance of the critical role played by relatives, friends, and co-workers in combating domestic violence.</p>]]></text>
